I have access to a second account which for now I have let lapse. Payment ran out on it on July 25 and it can still post. I was going to leave a message with it but that account was used by my nephew and his Chat name was too close to his user name... No use tempting anyone.... )<P>

<B>We're checking into why this might be the case now. It's probably a problem with information synchronizing with the database on the message board.<P>

Thanks for the info.<P>

-Gordon</b><P>

<HR align="center" width="75%"><P>

